item.title: Please help with adding models/items :(
item.dc:creator: @TrustedDealer TrustedDealer
item.description:
@TrustedDealer wrote:

Right what you wanna do:

  1. Go to your models file in your client files, put the models you downloaded in there and go onto your rsps and say “add models” or “add model MODELNUMBER”
    Then go the class8.java in your client files, put the ints for the model in there save compile and restart your client, spawn the item and BOOM!
    You have it…
